data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 17224 Brittle Ln, located in the serene and quiet Verona subdivision of Pflugerville, Texas. As you step into this remarkable 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, you will be invited to the grandeur of high ceilings that create an airy and spacious ambiance. This home opens up to a well-designed open concept floor plan, perfect for both entertaining and comfortable living. The heart of the home is a beautiful kitchen boasting a generously sized island, providing an ideal space for culinary creations and cherished memories. The expansive family room seamlessly connects, offering a cozy yet expansive area for relaxation and gatherings. A large walk-in pantry ensures you're well-stocked for any occasion. With a separate formal dining area and a dedicated breakfast nook, your hosting gatherings becomes a dream come true. The flexible layout allows you to effortlessly accommodate guests, family, and friends, ensuring everyone feels at home. The primary bedroom on the first floor, complete with an expansive en-suite, is a true retreat whereas the bathroom exudes sophistication, featuring beautiful vanities with undermount sinks, a separate walk-in shower, and a deep soaking tub for ultimate relaxation. Additionally, three well-proportioned guest bedrooms on the main floor, providing both convenience and accessibility caters perfectly to multi-generational living. Venture to the second floor with a spacious loft area. This versatile open space can be adapted to your needs such as another room, game room, media room and or office living. Outside, spacious covered patio invites you to enjoy the privacy and tranquility of the charming backyard. A 2-car garage provides ample space for your vehicles and storage needs. The proximity to Toll Roads 130 & 45 ensures seamless travel and provide all the conveniences you could desire. Don't miss the incredible opportunity to call this peaceful neighborhood your home. Call or Text or Email listing agent NOW
